reviewText: Taebo Live! Basic Volume 2 was recorded live at the Billy Blanks World Training Center and released in 1999. This is another good workout.

I was a bit disappointed with this VHS, even though it stated new, it didn't  look new upon viewing it.

Please verify with the seller that the quality is excellent before purchasing.

This is a basic work out video and you will only get out of it what you put into it.  If you are an expierence tae boer you will get nothing out of this tape. This is a basic tape and its easy to follow.  Its live and so there are mistakes but then its just like taking a class in the gym except you are at home!  AS a beginner workout its very good
